          "message": "\u26a0\ufe0f After high-flow O2, patient becomes increasingly drowsy. Repeat VBG: pH 7.22, pCO2 78. CO2 narcosis from over-oxygenation.",
          "recovery": "Reduce O2 to target 88-92%. Start BiPAP immediately. If no improvement, prepare for intubation.",
          "vitals": {
            "BP": "128/74",
            "HR": "88",
            "RR": "10",
            "Temp": "99.2\u00b0F",
            "SpO2": "99%"
          }
