          "teaching": "\u2705 Resuscitation before scope. Blood + PPI + GI consult. Glasgow-Blatchford score is high-risk. The ST depressions are demand ischemia (Type 2 MI) from anemia \u2014 NOT ACS. Treat the bleed, not the troponin."
