      "Continuing the antipsychotic because 'the patient needs it for their psych condition' \u2014 NMS is lethal, stop the drug",
      "Not checking CK \u2014 rhabdomyolysis is both diagnostic and the major cause of morbidity (AKI)",
      "Inadequate fluid resuscitation \u2014 these patients need massive volumes to prevent myoglobin-induced renal failure",
      "Attributing fever to infection without considering NMS in patients on antipsychotics",
      "Missing hyperkalemia from rhabdomyolysis \u2014 can cause fatal arrhythmia"
