          "aiPatientUpdate": "I feel calmer now. Less shaky. Everything was moving so fast before \u2014 I couldn't sit still and my legs kept jerking.",
          "teaching": "\u2705 SS vs NMS pearls: SS = clonus + hyperreflexia + agitation (serotonergic drugs). NMS = rigidity + bradykinesia + AMS (antipsychotic drugs). SS resolves faster (24-72h). Discharge when asymptomatic. Avoid serotonergic combinations in future."
