          "teaching": "\u2705 Hour-1 sepsis bundle: fluids + cultures + antibiotics + lactate. Lactate clearing (5.8\u21923.8). If MAP drops below 65 again \u2192 start norepinephrine. CT to rule out obstruction. Admit ICU. De-escalate abx once cultures return."
