          "teaching": "\u2705 Sodium corrected 6 mEq/L \u2014 approaching 24h limit of 8 mEq/L. STOP hypertonic saline. Monitor Na q2h. If overcorrecting, give DDAVP 2mcg IV + D5W (desmopressin clamp) to prevent osmotic demyelination syndrome."
